          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="moat-card">
          <div><span class="moat-tag grow">Growing moat</span></div>
          <div class="moat-info">
            <h4>Governance Position</h4>
            <p>Founding member of AAO with influence over protocol standards and framework evolution.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="moat-card">
          <div><span class="moat-tag hard">Hard to replicate</span></div>
          <div class="moat-info">
            <h4>Transaction Data Exhaust</h4>
