<!-- LEARN -->
<section class="section" id="learn">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:56px">
      <div class="section-tag" style="text-align:center">Learn</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Master the five protocols shaping AI advertising</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);font-size:16px;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto">Pievra is 100% free. No paid tiers, no credit card. Use the simulator to learn how cross-protocol campaigns work and build your expertise before the industry shifts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-name">AdCP & MCP</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Campaign negotiation and tool orchestration</div>
        <div style="margin:16px 0">
          <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.7">
            <p><strong>AdCP</strong> (Ad Context Protocol) enables AI agents to negotiate deals using natural language briefs instead of static rate cards. Stewarded by PubMatic, Scope3, Yahoo and Triton Digital.</p>
            <p style="margin-top:10px"><strong>MCP</strong> (Model Context Protocol) provides the universal tool-calling layer - agents query inventory, audiences and brand safety providers through a single adapter. Stewarded by Anthropic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://adcontextprotocol.org" target="_blank" class="price-cta light">Read AdCP Spec</a>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card featured">
        <div class="price-popular">Start Here</div>
        <div class="price-name" style="color:white">Simulate a Campaign</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Hands-on learning with the planner</div>
        <div style="margin:16px 0">
          <div style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.7">
            <p>Use the Campaign Planner to build a simulated cross-protocol media plan. See how budget splits across protocols, which agents are recommended, and download a professional PDF.</p>
            <p style="margin-top:10px">All features are free. No account limits. No upgrade walls.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#planner" class="price-cta teal">Open Campaign Planner</a>
      </div>
      <div class="price-card">
        <div class="price-name">UCP, ARTF & A2A</div>
        <div class="price-desc">Audience signals, real-time bidding and agent collaboration</div>
        <div style="margin:16px 0">
          <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.7">
            <p><strong>UCP</strong> activates privacy-safe audience signals as embeddings, replacing third-party cookies. <strong>ARTF</strong> extends OpenRTB for sub-100ms agentic auctions. <strong>A2A</strong> enables agents to collaborate in real time. Stewarded by IAB Tech Lab and Linux Foundation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://iabtechlab.com" target="_blank" class="price-cta light">Read IAB Specs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="txn-note">
      <p>Pievra is a <strong>free planning simulator and learning platform</strong>. No fees, no subscriptions. Campaign plans are simulations using verified market benchmarks and IAB-spec compliant data objects. <a href="/terms" style="color:var(--teal)">Terms of Service →</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

